<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about CAD)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/cat_cad.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2017 12:03:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>CAD练习题12——已知过一点和相切圆画圆</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-12-yi-zhi-guo-yi-dian-he-wai-qie-yuan-hua-yuan/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题知道圆过点、外切圆、半径，既不符合相切相切半径、也不符合三边相切。那么怎么画呢？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、由于过一点又知道半径，那么我们从这一点为圆心画圆，目标弧的圆心一定在这个圆上。同时又知道外切圆，所以圆心之间连线长度等于半径之和，所以一个圆半径是35，一个圆半径是50，总长度是85。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、上一步中两个圆的交点就是目标弧的圆心。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、同样的画法来画左边的80，但是注意这个是内切圆了，所以半径是减法，一个圆半径是80，一个圆半径是35，总长度是45。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p12-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-12-yi-zhi-guo-yi-dian-he-wai-qie-yuan-hua-yuan/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2017 11:47:14 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题11——利用平行和偏移作三角形内接花型图案</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-11-li-yong-ping-xing-he-pian-yi-zuo-san-jiao-xing-nei-jie-hua-xing-tu-an/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题看上去很难入手，先画三角形吧，不好找到内切的位置；先画花吧，不好找到外切的位置……&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用五边形画花。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、过五边形左右两个顶点和底边顶点，分别作三角形三边的平行线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、利用圆的半径，偏移上一步中的三条直线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、缩放图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p11-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-11-li-yong-ping-xing-he-pian-yi-zuo-san-jiao-xing-nei-jie-hua-xing-tu-an/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2017 11:16:45 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题10——利用平行作三角形的近似内接多边形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-10-li-yong-ping-xing-zuo-san-jiao-xing-de-jin-si-nei-jie-duo-bian-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题很容易想到画三角形的内切圆，但是得不到目标图形。所以，我们采用平行加缩放来作图。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先画出三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、从旁边画出五边形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、过五边形上边两个顶点和底边顶点，分别作三角形三条边的平行线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、缩放图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p10-5.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-10-li-yong-ping-xing-zuo-san-jiao-xing-de-jin-si-nei-jie-duo-bian-xing/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2017 11:10:53 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题9——较为复杂的利用圆作固定角度三角形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-9-jiao-wei-fu-za-de-li-yong-yuan-zuo-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-12.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-12.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题看上去较为复杂，但实际上还是利用圆作固定角度三角形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、画出明显已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、画出下半部分的90度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、作等分和旋转作垂线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、先处理右侧的72度，由于顶角是72度，所以作一条18度的斜线和过基线中点的垂线，以相交的点为圆心画圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、上一步的圆与最右侧垂线交于一点，连接三点，得到72度顶角。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、同样原理，得到其他三个角，注意每次基线长度是不同的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-9.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-9.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-10.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-10.PNG"&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-11.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-11.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-12.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p9-12.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-9-jiao-wei-fu-za-de-li-yong-yuan-zuo-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2017 11:01:53 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题8——利用圆作直角三角形和固定角度三角形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-8-li-yong-yuan-zuo-zhi-jiao-san-jiao-xing-he-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题的难点在于怎么画下面的90度和上面的75度，我们将用圆来解决这个问题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、画出明显已知的部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用直角三角形斜边中线等于斜边一半的原理，以斜边为直径画圆，确定直角的位置。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、作出等分点和垂线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、因为顶角是75度，作一条与基线是呈15度的斜线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、在基线的中点作一条垂线，与上一步中的斜线相交于一点，过这点画圆，与第3步中的垂线交于一点。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、连接三个已知点，得到75度顶角。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p8-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-8-li-yong-yuan-zuo-zhi-jiao-san-jiao-xing-he-gu-ding-jiao-du-san-jiao-xing/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2017 10:45:54 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题7——多边形和圆构成的对称图形</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-7-duo-bian-xing-he-yuan-gou-cheng-de-dui-cheng-tu-xing/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题没有给中等大小圆的半径，必然要用到三边相切画圆，而给了大圆的直径，必然要用到缩放。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、构造五边形顶点到对边连线延长线，为三边相切创造条件，进而画出中等大小圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、重复利用三边相切完成图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、缩放并清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p7-3.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-7-duo-bian-xing-he-yuan-gou-cheng-de-dui-cheng-tu-xing/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2017 11:33:01 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题6——已知圆心及所在直线和圆上的一条弦长画圆，画指定角度和长度的弦</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-6-yi-zhi-yuan-xin-suo-zai-zhi-xian-he-yi-tiao-xian-chang-hua-yuan-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-10.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-10.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题的难点主要有两个：已知圆心及所在直线和圆上的一条弦长，如何画圆；如何画一条指定角度和长度的弦。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、明显可画的部分比较少。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、因为已知弦长，所以利用平移二分之一弦长的方法，将圆心所在直线向两侧平移。即可得到圆上两点。类似的方法还可以用在角平分线环境中。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、在外部作一个等大的圆，画一条指定长度的水平弦，作图方法和上一步类似。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、旋转上一步的圆到指定角度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、移动外部圆，使得两圆重合，这道题的难点就解决了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、作等分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-7.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;8、作右侧的对称部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;9、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-9.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p6-9.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-6-yi-zhi-yuan-xin-suo-zai-zhi-xian-he-yi-tiao-xian-chang-hua-yuan-hua-zhi-ding-jiao-du-he-chang-du-de-xian/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2017 11:21:44 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题5——连续圆弧的画法</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-5-lian-xu-yuan-hu-de-hua-fa/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-8.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-8.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题看上去很乱，大部分都可以慢慢画出来，主要需要留意的是右侧上下对称的连续圆弧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先把明显的地方画好。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、处理上边的小圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、留意到，中间小圆与上边小圆连线为半径画的圆，正好是”蚕豆“中间的参考线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、相切相切半径画出整个“蚕豆”图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、处理右侧简单部分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6、处理连续圆弧，而连续圆弧的定位，靠的是与半径82.6圆的相切，现有条件下，如果没有这个相切，连续圆弧无法定位。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-7.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p5-7.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-5-lian-xu-yuan-hu-de-hua-fa/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2017 13:54:29 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题4——平行、垂直于切点的半径、相切相切半径画圆</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-4-ping-xing-chui-zhi-yu-qie-dian-de-ban-jing-xiang-qie-xiang-qie-ban-jing-hua-yuan/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-6.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-6.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题给了很多条件，大部分地方都比较容易，需要处理的是左边的40度和右边的80度，左边的40度可以利用平行来做，右边的80度可以利用垂直于切点的半径来做。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、先把明显的部分画出来。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用平行找角度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、相切相切半径画圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、利用垂直于切点的半径做固定角度的切线。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-4.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、完成图形，清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p4-5.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-4-ping-xing-chui-zhi-yu-qie-dian-de-ban-jing-xiang-qie-xiang-qie-ban-jing-hua-yuan/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2017 11:12:52 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CAD练习题3——顶点到对边垂线、三边相切画圆、缩放、阵列</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-3-ding-dian-dao-dui-bian-chui-xian-san-bian-xiang-qie-hua-yuan-suo-fang/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-5.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-5.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这道题只给了一个100，其他的条件都不明确。像这样的对称图形，都应优先考虑多边形的使用，再加上一圈都有圆弧相切，应能想到利用相切画圆，又由于无法确定半径，所以肯定要构造三边相切画圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、因为是七个花瓣，所以画一个七边形，利用顶点到对边垂线，构造三边相切画圆。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、利用镜像或者阵列，得到一圈图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-2.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-2.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、清理图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-3.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-3.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、画中心的圆，连接垂线，缩放图形。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-4.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/p3-4.PNG"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>CAD</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/cadlian-xi-ti-3-ding-dian-dao-dui-bian-chui-xian-san-bian-xiang-qie-hua-yuan-suo-fang/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2017 10:28:45 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>